  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether cleft palate repair increases the risk for
      obstructive sleep apnea in children and whether sleep apnea could explain learning and
      behavior difficulties that are often observed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
